Installation

    git clone git://github.com/chrisweibel/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symklinks
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
    
Notes:
    For the jslint had to replace jslint-core with latest
    https://raw.github.com/douglascrockford/JSLint/master/jslint.js
